  "text": "I'll ask this question to inform me a little bit about what you just stated. When you came to this planet in craft 18, 000 and 11, 000 years ago, these craft have been called, I believe, bell craft and were photographed by George Adamski. If I am correct these craft looked somewhat like a bell; they had portholes around the upper portions; and they had three hemispheres at 120° apart underneath. Is this correct? I am Ra. This is correct.",
